<text top="957" left="81" width="12" height="18" font="0">2.</text>
<text top="957" left="93" width="5" height="18" font="9"> </text>
<text top="957" left="134" width="657" height="18" font="0">Post Order-The schedule of drawing/ data submission shall be mutually agreed between EIL &amp; the </text>
